$= f'(x)g(x) + f(x)g'(x)$

2. Quotient rule
$lim_(h->0) frac(w(x+h)-w(x), h) = lim_(h->0) frac(f(x+h)/g(x+h) - f(x)/g(x), h)=$
$lim_(h->0) frac((f(x+h)g(x))/(g(x+h)g(x)) - (f(x)g(x+h))/(g(x+h)g(x)), h) = lim_(h->0) frac((f(x+h)g(x)-f(x)g(x+h))/ (g(x)g(x+h)), h)$\

